@booksUrl = http://localhost:8080
@bookId = REEMPLAZA_CON_UUID_REAL

### Listar todos los libros
GET {{booksUrl}}/api/books

### Buscar libros por título
GET {{booksUrl}}/api/books?title=Java

### Buscar libros por autor
GET {{booksUrl}}/api/books?author=Robert

### Buscar libros por ISBN
GET {{booksUrl}}/api/books?isbn=978-1234567890

### Buscar libro por ID
GET {{booksUrl}}/api/books/{{bookId}}

### Crear libro
POST {{booksUrl}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code",
  "author": "Robert C. Martin",
  "category": "Programacion",
  "isbn": "978-0132350884"
}

### Actualizar libro
PUT {{booksUrl}}/api/books/{{bookId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code Updated",
  "author": "Robert C. Martin",
  "category": "Programacion",
  "isbn": "978-0132350884"
}

### Eliminar libro
DELETE {{booksUrl}}/api/books/{{bookId}}
